OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy across much England and
OL,6,FWales. A few spots of light rain
OL,7,Fpossible, mainly in the west. Sunnier
OL,8,Fskies for Scotland and Northern
OL,9,FIreland, though cloud and rain moving
OL,10,Finto the northwest later. Feeling
OL,11,Fpleasant in the sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy and damp across
OL,14,FEngland and Wales, with outbreaks of
OL,15,Fpatchy rain. Clearer skies for
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland and much of Scotland.
OL,17,FThough breezy with some rain across
OL,18,Fthe far northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
